g.text: Request capsule availability from Sensing Subsystem
Forward sensor data to Safety Subsystem
Send DISPENSE command to Actuation Subsystem
Send sensor readings and redundancy data to Control Subsystem
Send updated reading to Control Subsystem
Move servo motor to release capsule
Send updated count to MQTT server
Log dispense event to WWW server
